  <h1>Look A Poem by Anita Kuno</h1>
  <div class="sidenote">A place for me to post my poetry whenever the muse whispers in my ear.
    <ul>
      <li><a href="../index.html">Home<a></li>
      <li><a href="poetry.html">Twitter Poems</a></li>
      <li><a href="look_a_poem.html">Look A Poem</a></li>
      <li><a href="look_another_poem.html">Look Another Poem</a></li>
      <li><a href="and_another_poem.html">And Another Poem</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
<p>cat in my lap<br />
paws across my wrist<br /> 
heavy<br />
she doesn't seem to mind the dance that is me typing</p>

<p>sunlight streams<br />
across the floor<br />
up the walls<br />
makes the plies of books<br />
look sculptural</p>

<p>birds singing<br />
outside my house<br />
quietly<br />
adding their music<br />
to the day</p>

<p>leaves larger<br />
more green<br />
puffs of tender membrane<br />
umbrella out<br />
stretch to the sun</p>
  </body>
